This repository contains the open-source ScriptScore client: the Python CLI/runtime, JSON-RPC sidecar, Tauri desktop host, Svelte/SvelteKit frontend, public documentation, and related build/compliance tooling.

The ScriptScore client is licensed under AGPL-3.0-only. See LICENSE for the full license text.

ScriptScorePlus is a separate hosted API service. Hosted service implementation details are not included in this repository. The public client may contain safe client-side request types, provider selection values, or coming-soon UI for hosted API support.

Third-party dependencies retain their own licenses. Generate and review third-party notices and dependency inventory before distributing release artifacts. The desktop build expects bundled notices under desktop/dist/legal/.
